get.description:
if email field is provided along with any other field, then search
would be performed by email only.

When searching by alternate id, provide both key and exact value to search.
The only alternate_id key currently supported for external clients is "clientUserId".
To search a user with internal client's user id of "X1KJ4" (an example), the request in json format should be:

{

     "alternateId": {
           "clientUserId": "X1KJ4"  
     }

}
